### Add or update review (only customers who purchased the product)
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "productId": 18,
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Great product",
  "body": "Worked exactly as described"
}

### Get reviews for a product
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/product/18
Content-Type: application/json

### Get my reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/myreviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Update a review
PATCH http://localhost:3000/reviews/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "id": 3,
  "rating": 4,
  "title": "Updated title",
  "body": "Updated body"
}

### Delete a review
DELETE http://localhost:3000/reviews/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "id": 3
}